Source: sdl2-image-2-0-4-0
Version: 2.0.4
Build-Depends: sdl2-2-0-9-1-0, libpng-1-6-36-1-0
Description: SDL_image is an image file loading library. It loads images as SDL surfaces and textures, and supports the following formats: BMP, GIF, JPEG, LBM, PCX, PNG, PNM, TGA, TIFF, WEBP, XCF, XPM, XV

Feature: libjpeg-turbo
Description: Support for JPEG image format
Build-Depends: libjpeg-turbo-1-5-3-2-0

Feature: tiff
Description: Support for TIFF image format
Build-Depends: tiff-4-0-10-2-0

Feature: libwebp
Description: Support for WEBP image format.
Build-Depends: libwebp-1-0-2-1-0
